title: 820-00165-A
message:
Using original Magsafe 2 charger?

Check PM_BATLOW_L, PCH_DSWVRMEN, PM_DSW_PWRGD, SMC_ADAPTER_EN, PM_PWRBTN_L, PM_RSMRST_L and the 4 PCH's RTC (DC) signals.
Trigger SMC_ONOFF_L and check for drop pulse at PM_PWRBTN_L (at same time).
